<plot>During the Battle of the Bugle in the winter of 1944, three soldiers are sent on a simple reconnaissance patrol to send a message to their battalion's command post. They encounter fierce enemy resistance and are pinned down, lost somewhere between their own and the German frontline. With the sun set, they are forced to spend the night somewhere near the main line of resistance, and reflect on their pasts, presents and futures.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?052965</url></doc>
